Speaker 2: Okay, let's take a look and see what's going on. Is this your phone number on file?

Speaker 1: Sure, yes.

Speaker 2: Okay, so yeah, that was just one of your refills that went up there, sir.

Speaker 1: You do not have to get them that way. You can choose when you get your refills.

Speaker 2: Correct.

Speaker 1: So I didn't order, I just got charged a second time.

Speaker 2: Yeah, so I'm assuming it's because when you first order this,

Speaker 1: you've got to set it up to either like to just get it once, order as needed,

Speaker 2: or, you know, to get it at whatever frequency you would like.

Speaker 1: If it's not done, it'll kind of go out how the doctor writes it according to the pills that you ordered.

Speaker 2: I think that's what happened here.

Speaker 1: But, you know, we can definitely change that so that does not happen going forward.

Speaker 2: Correct. I didn't even use so far, you know, I didn't have girls for some time, you know,

Speaker 1: so I don't need it right now, you know.

Speaker 2: Correct.

Speaker 1: If you can just return that money on my account and I'm going to order as I need.

Speaker 2: Okay, so basically how that works, sir, we're just going to,

Speaker 1: so like the next four months here we won't bill you or send you anything,

Speaker 2: you're going to have to call to get your next order in like the next four months.

Speaker 1: Does that work for you?

Speaker 2: Yeah, I mean, I can order when I need.

Speaker 1: Could be two months, could be three months, could be, you know, could be one month.

Speaker 2: Well, yeah, so basically what we do is we just keep your prescription available,

Speaker 1: say for five months.

Speaker 2: If you need more time, let us know.

Speaker 1: But the prescription doesn't stay open forever,

Speaker 2: so we can keep it open for you for the next five months and you would have to call us for your next one.

Speaker 1: If you need more time, then let us know as well.

Speaker 2: I can give you my extension and my name here, and that way you can call me directly.

Speaker 1: I can do that for you.

Speaker 2: Sure, I am ready.

Speaker 1: Okay, so the name is Quinn, Q-U-I-N-N.

Speaker 2: Can you start again, please?

Speaker 1: That's okay.

Speaker 2: Q-U-I-N-N.

Speaker 1: Quinn.

Speaker 2: Yes, sir.

Speaker 1: And the number, the phone number is?

Speaker 2: The extension number is 0035.

Speaker 1: 0035.

Speaker 2: Okay, I just want to make sure.

Speaker 1: So I got the first order.

Speaker 2: It's over there waiting, and you are going to return this money on my account,

Speaker 1: and I'm going to give you a call when I'm ready, correct?

Speaker 2: Correct.

Speaker 1: Correct.

Speaker 2: Okay, so I'm waiting for this to return to my account.

Speaker 1: Okay, thank you, Quinn.

Speaker 2: You're welcome.

Speaker 2: Bye.
